4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive bootcamp to become an AI Machine Learning Engineer over 16 weeks. No prior experience is needed to embark on a career as a data scientist, where students will learn essential skills such as Python, SQL, and statistics. The course focuses on creating and deploying predictive models, utilizing tools like Pandas and Numpy, and mastering algorithms for supervised and unsupervised learning. Classes are limited to 12 participants and taught in English or Spanish. Graduates receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop